WEBVTT

00:02:58.917 --> 00:03:00.446
they enjoy the ensuing thrill,

00:03:00.446 --> 00:03:03.446
even if the immediate sensation is unpleasant.

00:03:03.446 --> 00:03:04.756
Some studies have even shown

00:03:04.756 --> 00:03:06.215
that those who like to eat hot stuff

00:03:06.215 --> 00:03:08.926
are more likely to enjoy other adrenaline-rich activities,

00:03:08.926 --> 00:03:10.554
like gambling.

00:03:10.554 --> 00:03:11.969
The taste for spicy food

00:03:11.969 --> 00:03:13.598
may even be genetic.

00:03:13.598 --> 00:03:15.558
And if you're thinking about training a bit,

00:03:15.558 --> 00:03:17.059
to up your tolerance for spice,

00:03:17.059 --> 00:03:18.112
know this:

00:03:18.112 --> 00:03:19.396
According to some studies,

00:03:19.396 --> 00:03:21.231
the pain doesn't get any better.

00:03:21.231 --> 00:03:22.946
You just get tougher.

00:03:22.946 --> 00:03:24.612
In fact, researchers have found

00:03:24.612 --> 00:03:26.445
that people who like to eat spicy foods

00:03:26.445 --> 00:03:29.029
don't rate the burn any less painful

00:03:29.029 --> 00:03:30.612
than those who don't.